---
// Importa el video de fondo
import videoBackground from '~/assets/images/hero2.mp4'; // Asegúrate de tener el video en la ruta correcta
---

<div class="relative w-full h-screen overflow-hidden entry-effect-1">
  <!-- Video de fondo -->
  <video autoplay muted loop playsinline class="absolute inset-0 object-cover w-full h-full z-0">
    <source src={videoBackground} type="video/mp4" />
    Tu navegador no soporta videos.
  </video>

  <!-- Contenedor del contenido -->
  <div class="relative flex flex-col justify-center items-center h-full text-white text-center p-10 z-10 entry-effect-2 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('/ruta/a/imagen-de-respaldo.jpg');">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 drop-shadow-lg animate__animated animate__fadeInDown">
      Innovación y Tecnología para Tu Éxito
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-6 drop-shadow-md max-w-3xl animate__animated animate__fadeInUp">
      Descubre cómo nuestras soluciones avanzadas pueden transformar tu negocio y llevarlo al siguiente nivel.
    </p>
    
    <!-- Botones -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row space-y-4 sm:space-y-0 sm:space-x-4 animate__animated animate__fadeIn">
      <button class="open-modal-btn px-8 py-3 rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-purple-600 hover:from-blue-600 hover:to-purple-700 transition duration-300 text-white shadow-lg">
        Empieza Ahora
      </button>
      <a href="https://wa.me/56963238857?text=Hola,%20me%20gustaría%20recibir%20más%20información" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center bg-[#25D366] text-white px-4 py-3 rounded-lg transition duration-300 hover:bg-[#20B357] shadow-lg">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" class="mr-2">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 21l1.65 -3.8a9 9 0 1 1 3.4 2.9l-5.05 .9" />
          <path d="M9 10a.5 .5 0 0 0 1 0v-1a.5 .5 0 0 0 -1 0v1a5 5 0 0 0 5 5h1a.5 .5 0 0 0 0 -1h-1a.5 .5 0 0 0 0 1" />
        </svg>
        <span>Contacta a un Asesor</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
